        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
            <head>Scope and Content </head>
            <p>Discusses the receipt of a shipment of various articles from his father's estate,
                including wine; also lists items, including scientific apparatus, not yet received.
                Sends greet ings to various persons in Williamsburg, including Mrs. Dawson
                *Elizabeth Dawson, widow of William Dawson, president of the College of William and
                Mary!. </p>
